Summary: Watched a star size item streak across sky
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile I was out with my dogs, I noticed a star like shape streak across the sky the noon was at about 1130 oclock over head..Military location (12 oclock is directly over head venus was at about 130 oclock at a sw location, star like light streaked in between the moon and venus, time i was watching was about 2 seconds size was about that of the lead of a #2 pencil, after 2 seconds it vanished
